#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.155"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.155:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.155:0.2"
msgid "16. Saddhammavagga "
msgstr "16. The True Teaching "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.155:0.3"
msgid "155. Dutiyasaddhammasammosasutta "
msgstr "155. The Decline of the True Teaching (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.155:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these five things lead to the decline and disappearance of the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an5.155:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.155:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhū dhammaṃ na pariyāpuṇanti—"
msgstr "It’s when the mendicants don’t memorize the teaching—"

msgctxt "an5.155:1.4"
msgid "suttaṃ, geyyaṃ, veyyākaraṇaṃ, gāthaṃ, udānaṃ, itivuttakaṃ, jātakaṃ, abbhutadhammaṃ, vedallaṃ. "
msgstr "statements, songs, discussions, verses, inspired exclamations, legends, stories of past lives, amazing stories, and classifications. "

msgctxt "an5.155:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the first thing that leads to the decline and disappearance of the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.155:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na vitthārena paresaṃ desenti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants don’t explain the teaching in detail to others as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:2.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the second thing … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
#. VAR: paraṃ → paresaṃ (bj, s1, km, pts1) | pare (?)
msgctxt "an5.155:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na vitthārena paraṃ vācenti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants don’t make others recite the teaching in detail as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:3.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the third thing … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an5.155:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na vitthārena sajjhāyaṃ karonti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants don’t recite the teaching in detail as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:4.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fourth thing … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an5.155:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ na cetasā anuvitakkenti anuvicārenti manasānupekkhanti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants don’t think about and consider the teaching in their hearts, examining it with their minds as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:5.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fifth thing that leads to the decline and disappearance of the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.155:5.3"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "These five things lead to the decline and disappearance of the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.178, sc6
msgctxt "an5.155:6.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "These five things lead to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an5.155:6.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.155:6.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhū dhammaṃ pariyāpuṇanti—"
msgstr "It’s when the mendicants memorize the teaching—"

msgctxt "an5.155:6.4"
msgid "suttaṃ, geyyaṃ, veyyākaraṇaṃ, gāthaṃ, udānaṃ, itivuttakaṃ, jātakaṃ, abbhutadhammaṃ, vedallaṃ. "
msgstr "statements, songs, discussions, verses, inspired exclamations, legends, stories of past lives, amazing stories, and classifications. "

msgctxt "an5.155:6.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the first thing that leads to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an5.155:7.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ vitthārena paresaṃ desenti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants explain the teaching in detail to others as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:7.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the second thing … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an5.155:8.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ vitthārena paraṃ vācenti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants make others recite the teaching in detail as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:8.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the third thing … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an5.155:9.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ vitthārena sajjhāyaṃ karonti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants recite the teaching in detail as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:9.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fourth thing … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an5.155:10.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ cetasā anuvitakkenti anuvicārenti manasānupekkhanti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, the mendicants think about and consider the teaching in their hearts, examining it with their minds as they learned and memorized it. "

msgctxt "an5.155:10.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "This is the fifth thing that leads to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.155:10.3"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These five things lead to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the true teaching.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.155:10.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

